This README file contains information on using the igep-tools
package. Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Table of Contents
=================

   I. Overwiew
  II. Installation (TODO)


I. Overview
=========================================

This is a suite of shell scripts (and a set of helper programs that you may use
if you wish) Invoking the shell script without any arguments will display help
screens for each program. Please use that interface for detailed help.

  init/
    rc.init - init.d startup script
  scripts/
    create-android-image - Tool that helps users create an Android image tarball
                           from Android build.
    igep-flash           - Tool to flash the firmware to the OneNAND/NAND
    igep-media-create    - Tool that helps users to automatically create a bootable
                           microSD from a image.


